label.value: research authorization for post mortem specimen donation was obtained

definition.value: An information content entity that indicates whether research authorization  for post mortem specimen donation was obtained.

label.value: research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation that is affirmative

definition.value: A research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation establishing agreement for post-mortem donation and use in general research.

label.value: research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation that is negative

definition.value: A research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation establishing the lack of agreement for post-mortem donation and use in general research.

label.value: research authorization for post mortem specimen donation not obtained due to religious reasons

definition.value: A research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation in which the reason authorization was not obtained was due to due to religious reasons.

label.value: research authorization for post mortem specimen donation not obtained due to surgeon's recommendation

definition.value: A research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation in which authorization was not obtained because the donors surgeon did not recommend it.

label.value: research authorization for post mortem specimen donation not obtained because legally authorized representative felt pressured

definition.value: A research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation because the legally authorized representative felt pressured into making a decision.

label.value: research authorization for post mortem specimen donation not obtained because legally authorized representative felt too distraught

definition.value: A research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation in which authorization was not obtained because the the legally authorized representative felt too distraught.

label.value: research authorization for post mortem specimen donation not obtained because legally authorized representative needed more time to make a decision

definition.value: A research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation in which authorization was not obtained because the the legally authorized representative needed more time to make a decision.

label.value: research authorization for post mortem specimen donation not obtained because legally authorized representative was uncomfortable with the risks

definition.value: A research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation in which authorization was not obtained because the the legally authorized representative was uncomfortable with the risks of the request.

label.value: research authorization for post mortem specimen donation not obtained because legally authorized representative was afraid the decision might affect the surgery plans of donor

definition.value: A research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation in which authorization was not obtained because the the legally authorized representative was afraid the decision might affect the surgery plans for the donor.

label.value: research authorization for post mortem specimen donation not obtained because legally authorized representative did not agree with the activity of biobanking

definition.value: A research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation in which authorization was not obtained because the the legally authorized representative did not agree with the activity of biobanking.

label.value: research authorization for post mortem specimen donation not obtained because legally authorized representative did not show up to the appointment as scheduled

definition.value: A research authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation in which authorization was not obtained because the the legally authorized representative did not show up to the appointment as scheduled.

label.value: date of research protocol approval as determined by an institutional review board

definition.value: A data item that indicates the calendar date on which a research protocol was approved by an Institutional Review Board related to where the research will take place.

label.value: date of research protocol expiration as determined by an institutional review board

definition.value: A data item that indicates the calendar date on which a research protocol expires and becomes inactive as determined by an Institutional Review Board.

label.value: identification number of a protocol at a particular site

definition.value: An centrally registered identifier symbol assigned by an Institutional Review Board (IRB) that identifies a particular protocol at a given site.

label.value: date that research authorization for post mortem specimen donation was witnessed

definition.value: A data item that indicates the calendar date on which the signing  of the research authorization for post mortem specimen donation by the legally authorized individual was witnessed.

label.value: date of research authorization verification

definition.value: A data item that indicates the calendar date on which the receipt of the research authorization was verified by study personnel.

label.value: name of person screening specimen donors

definition.value: A personal name that designates who performed the screening of a potential specimen donor for a research study.

label.value: name of person obtaining authorization from legally authorized representative for post-mortem specimen donation

definition.value: A personal name of an individual with research obtainer role who approaches a person's legal representative and informs them of key facts about potential risks and benefits, and asks them for authorization for post-mortem specimen donation  for research for the person they legally represent.

label.value: date on which research authorization was obtained from legally authorized representative

definition.value: A data item that indicates the calendar date on which a research authorization was obtained from a specimen donor's legally authorized representative.

label.value: identifier for legally authorized representative

definition.value: An identifier that uniquely identifies a particular legally authorized representative in a research study.

label.value: relationship between person signing research authorization and specimen donor

definition.value: A relationship that may be biological or legal, between the specimen donor and the legally authorized representative who signed the research authorization.

label.value: specimen donor's date of birth

definition.value: A date of birth that signifies the calendar date on which a particular donor of a specimen was born.

label.value: donor's biological sex

definition.value: Biological sex of the person who bears the role of donor.

label.value: post mortem  donor role

definition.value: A role borne by a person who has died from whom specimens are collected.

label.value: age of specimen donor at time that authorization from legally authorized representative was obtained

definition.value: An age measurement datum that indicates the age of the specimen donor at the time that authorization from their legally authorized representative was obtained.

label.value: indicator of whether specimen donor has reached the age of majority

definition.value: An Information content entity that indicates whether the specimen donor  has reached the age of majority as defined by the appropriate regulation.

label.value: comments related to research authorization process

definition.value: A textual entity that provides additional information that may be relevant to the research authorization verification process.

label.value: willingness to be contacted for a research study

definition.value: An information content entity that signifies the willingness of an individual to be contacted for a research study.

label.value: agreement to a specified research addendum

definition.value: An authorization documentation in which a legally authorized individual  agrees to a specific research addendum for the person they represent.

label.value: authorization documentation for postmortem specimen donation for a specified purpose

definition.value: An authorization documentation for postmortem specimen donation in which specimens are to be used for a specified purpose (e.g., transplantation, research, education).

label.value: authorization for postmortem specimen donation for transplantation purposes only

definition.value: An authorization documentation for postmortem specimen donation for a specified purpose which is solely for the purpose of transplantation to another person or persons.

label.value: authorization for postmortem specimen donation for transplantation and research

definition.value: An authorization documentation for postmortem specimen donation for a specified purpose which is for transplantation, research, education and the advancement of science.

label.value: authorization not obtained for whole brain donation

definition.value: An authorization documentation for post mortem specimen donation in which authorization is not obtained for whole brain donation.

label.value: limitations on research authorization for use of donated specimens

definition.value: An authorization documentation for postmortem specimen donation in which authorization includes specific limitations or additional information related to the use of tissue for research.

label.value: presence of metastatic tumor exclusion criterion

definition.value: An exclusion criterion that defines whether a metastatic tumor is present, which if met, makes an individual unsuitable for a given task or participation in a given process.

label.value: presence of a tumor larger than a specified size exclusion criterion

definition.value: An exclusion criterion that defines whether a tumor is larger than a specified size, which if met, makes an individual unsuitable for a given task or participation in a given process.

label.value: authorization to collect of minimum number of organ/tissue types for a specific study inclusion criterion

definition.value: An inclusion criterion that defines whether the specimen donor has provided authorization to allow for the minimum number of organs/tissue types for a specific study to be collected, which when met, makes a  specimen donor suitable for a given task or participation in a given process.

label.value: tissue collection timing and placed in fixative inclusion criterion

definition.value: An inclusion criterion that is defined by whether it is likely that tissue collection can be started AND the first tissue can be placed in fixative within a specified period of time from cardiac cessation or recorded time of death (observed or presumed) for a specimen donor, which if met, makes a specimen donor suitable for a given task or participation in a given process.

label.value: time since radiation therapy was received prior to surgery

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time elapsed since radiation therapy prior to surgery.

label.value: time since chemotherapy was received prior to surgery

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time elapsed since chemotherapy prior to surgery.

label.value: time since immunotherapy was received prior to surgery

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time elapsed since immunotherapy prior to surgery.

label.value: time since hormonal therapy was received prior to surgery

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time elapsed since hormonal therapy prior to surgery.

label.value: date of radiation therapy prior to surgery

definition.value: A data item that reports the calendar date when radiation therapy was received prior to surgery.

label.value: date of chemotherapy prior to surgery

definition.value: A data item that reports the calendar date when chemotherapy was received prior to surgery.

label.value: date of immunotherapy prior to surgery

definition.value: A data item that reports the calendar date when immunotherapy was received prior to surgery.

label.value: date of hormonal therapy prior to surgery

definition.value: A data item that reports the calendar date when hormonal therapy was received prior to surgery.

label.value: lifelong non-drinker of alcohol

definition.value: An Alcohol Use History in which there is no alcohol consumption.

label.value: current non-drinker of alcohol

definition.value: An Alcohol Use History in which there was alcohol consumption in the past but is currently a non-drinker of alcohol.

label.value: moderate alcohol consumption history

definition.value: An Alcohol Use History in which alcohol consumption was equal to or less than 2 drinks per day for men and 1 drink or less per day for women.
